These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, october, april, march, february, august, may
1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in october##2
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| Birthday   | march | may | september | august | april | february | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, australian, thai, colombian, indonesian, pakistani, argentine
1. the colombian is on the left of the thai##1
2. the indonesian is on the far left##1
3. the australian is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the indonesian is on the left of the brazilian##1
6. the pakistani is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Nationality   | indonesian | brazilian | pakistani | australian | colombian | thai | argentine |

