.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-3::.
7 different games are played: scrabble, go, poker, chess, domino, monopoly, snooker
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
4. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing domino##1
7. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
8. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |      3      |         4          |      5       |     6     |    7    |
| Game   | go | chess | scrabble | domino | snooker | poker | monopoly |

