.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, blend, pall-mall, cain, bluemaster, swisher, oliveros
1. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
3. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
8. the cain-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Cigar   | siglo | oliveros | cain | swisher | bluemaster | pall-mall | blend |

