1. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
6. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3    |    4     |   5   |   6   |   7    |
| Pet   | pony | goldfish | horse | cat | hamster | bird | guinea-pig |

