.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: gospel, classical, punk, trance, techno, reggae, jazz
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of trance is the fan of trance##1
5. the fan of jazz is between the fan of punk and the fan of reggae##2
6. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
7. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2    |    3     |  4  |   5   |    6     |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | trance | techno | reggae | jazz | punk | classical |

