5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
