.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
House: ranch-style, art-deco, victorian, colonial, modern, palace, tower
 1. the modern house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 2. the tower house is on the left of the colonial house##1
 3. the modern house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 4. the modern house is in an odd position##4
 5. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 6. the modern house is on the left of the victorian house##1
 7. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 8. the palace house is in an odd position##4
 9. the colonial house is on the left or right of the modern house##3
10. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| House   | art-deco | ranch-style | tower | colonial | modern | victorian | palace |

 